A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Code Section 20-2B-23 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to
2 requirements for participating schools, responsibilities of education savings authority,
3 prohibited requirements, and agency not established, so as to require participating schools
4 to prepare school safety plans that meet certain requirements; to provide for related matters;
5 to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
6 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
7 SECTION 1.
8 Code Section 20-2B-23 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to requirements
9 for participating schools, responsibilities of education savings authority, prohibited
10 requirements, and agency not established, is amended by adding a new subsection to read as
11 follows:
12 "(h) Each participating school shall prepare a school safety plan that meets the
13 requirements for school safety plans of public schools as set forth in Code Section
14 20-2-1185."
